Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_spu::_br_pmd_status

The lane fields in this register are indexed by logical PCS lane ID. The lane 0 field (LN0_*) is valid for both 10GBASE-R and 40GBASE-R. The remaining fields (LN1_*, LN2_*, LN3_*) are only valid for 40GBASE-R.
